	<div style="text-align:right;">
		KUSTER, Laura Helena Teixeira<sup>1</sup>; GONCALVES, Oksandro Osdival<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa CNPq-PIBIC		<BR>
